### Get all ciders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ciders

### Get a cider by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ciders/{id}

### Create a new cider
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ciders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 999,
  "nazwa": "aaaNew Cidear",
  "styl": "Półsłodki",
  "cena": -25.0
}

### Get all producers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/producers

### Get a producer by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/producers/{id}

